{"tid":1631022,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求下你地發夢唔好再係ig po story","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:35:23.000Z","uid":209896,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"591a558c236bb3f4c0c213748c00a1fc49b6b357","tid":1631022,"uid":209896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:28:15.000Z","msg":"每次發夢手足唔好彩俾狗咬都會有一堆人叫幫手report手足ig<br />\n老實講次次都用晒我有既account黎report<br />\n但report左咁多個 最後都冇個成功俾ig封<br />\n求下大家發夢唔好再po ig story<br />\n發夢唔係打卡位 有ig story俾位狗入真係唔抵架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n香港人反抗！<br />\n核爆都唔撚割！"},{"pid":"816d0dedd8c5ab15e095429286eff15371acb2e4","tid":1631022,"uid":130079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:29:00.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"d1635ccd10010a8e60478548efcd6886358fe914","tid":1631022,"uid":209896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:30:48.000Z","msg":"自推先1/10"},{"pid":"84a080b2da7d6c6dcdc748bc1b93e1619a023dad","tid":1631022,"uid":209896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:31:01.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"6db09525dd6e67ad0905ed6c56e780bf74bfa467","tid":1631022,"uid":209896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:31:28.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"30a9fc328cfab7694bbe91b2dcbc3162e0710a7f","tid":1631022,"uid":209896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:31:41.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"a0c3eb8c59b0440863a611cc1bc2c9af821de1f1","tid":1631022,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:31:42.000Z","msg":"唔Po ig 人地點知我有出去發夢呀"},{"pid":"a26c6db8095aed7765efb22a411c5b5c357eef15","tid":1631022,"uid":209896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:31:52.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"d269ae4b9bac89416e22be2cfec2ed19ca929cc1","tid":1631022,"uid":209896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"3b1fbec598562c923982d7d9ff9a628f9ad44e12","tid":1631022,"uid":159762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:32:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港警察濫權實錄資料庫</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL5Urr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=8bf1d74d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有英文同日文版 大家落力share俾更多外國人睇！！</span>"},{"pid":"c614c4e951d9721f87e2ea614142023fb83a69e4","tid":163102